title: Kbd
description: show keyboard shortcuts and key combinations
---

{% from "components/kbd/macro.njk" import kbd %}

<h2>Default</h2>
<p>Press {{ kbd({ text: "Esc", label: "Escape" }) }} to close the
  dialog.</p>

<p>Press {{ kbd({ text: "Ctrl" }) }} + {{ kbd({ text: "S" }) }} to
  save.</p>

<h2>Mac modifiers with accessible labels</h2>
<p>Press
  {{ kbd({ text: "⌘", label: "Command" }) }} +
  {{ kbd({ text: "⇧", label: "Shift" }) }} +
  {{ kbd({ text: "P" }) }}
  to open the command palette.</p>

<h2>Arrow keys</h2>
<p>Use
  {{ kbd({ text: "↑", label: "Up arrow" }) }}
  {{ kbd({ text: "↓", label: "Down arrow" }) }}
  to move between options.</p>
